cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL

The paper proposes a novel convolutional neural network-based approach for white matter tract segmentation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The approach also involves deep learning techniques such as neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of natural language processing (cs.CL) for data analysis.
